                    <li>Stories can be created in seconds which would require minutes using actual issue tracker.</li>
                    <li>Preparing roadmaps for projects.</li>
                    <li>Prioritizing and filtering stories.</li>
                    <li>Grouping stories by themes, epics, release and sprints.</li>
                    <li>Preparing and sharing estimates to customer.</li>
