        <li>Importing stories using xml ,excel or csv files.</li>
        <li>Serialisation and storing fields in database based on projects. At presents it needs to be selected or deselected from column chooser every time.</li>
        <li>User story mapper module to get birds eye view of project.</li>
        <li>Kanban boards for roadmaps, priority, release and sprint plans.</li>
    </ul>
</div>


